00:34:47.500 --> 00:34:51.000
this is Her pure desire. And for this pure desire

00:34:51.291 --> 00:34:54.500
She is striving very hard every moment. And in this

00:34:54.917 --> 00:34:58.000
you have all earned it, achieved it, accepted with love,

00:34:58.333 --> 00:35:01.333
and going ahead you have progressed in it.

