00:35:13.250 --> 00:35:15.250
How much Sita had to suffer, how much Radha

00:35:15.667 --> 00:35:18.959
had to suffer, how much Mary had to suffer:

00:35:19.250 --> 00:35:21.500
I forget all that past. I feel

00:35:21.834 --> 00:35:24.500
as if nothing has happened in the past, and that

00:35:24.999 --> 00:35:27.417
whatever is happening now is something special.

00:35:27.834 --> 00:35:31.542
