00:35:35.834 --> 00:35:37.959
- in human form. But the Devi which we call

00:35:38.250 --> 00:35:40.792
as Shri Mahakali has not incarnated in human form.

00:35:41.166 --> 00:35:43.333
She always existed in the form of a Devi.

00:35:43.834 --> 00:35:46.583
That is why to come in the form of Devi is easy,

00:35:47.000 --> 00:35:49.959
but to come in the form of a human being is very

00:35:50.250 --> 00:35:53.208
difficult task. And to fight like a human being and

00:35:53.542 --> 00:35:56.583
live with the human beings is even more difficult.

00:35:56.999 --> 00:36:00.333
