00:36:01.750 --> 00:36:03.959
is much more difficult. All this work in the form of human

00:36:04.417 --> 00:36:07.875
beings was done by all the Devas, and today we are experiencing

00:36:08.208 --> 00:36:11.917
the auspicious fruits of all the work done in the past.

00:36:12.291 --> 00:36:15.750
